{"id":202099,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/加拿大退出《京都议定书》，中国谴责/","date":"2011-12-14T07:00:27Z","modified":"2011-12-14T07:00:27Z","title":"加拿大退出《京都议定书》，中国谴责","content":"<p>加拿大宣布退出《京都议定书》，环境部长肯特（Peter Kent）称，《京都议定书》不包含世界上最大的两个温室气体排放国-美国和中国，“这样是不可能有效果的”，他强调说，加拿大排放的温室气体不足全球总排放量的2%，他表示如果阻止气候变化的问题对每个国家都是公平的，那么加拿大愿意担负着相应的责任。中国外交部发言人刘伟民对此表示遗憾，官方新华社则谴责加拿大推卸责任。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1aed432e/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E3%80%8A%E4%BA%AC%E9%83%BD%E8%AE%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F12%2F14%2F034209%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/12/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E3%80%8A%E4%BA%AC%E9%83%BD%E8%AE%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F12%2F14%2F034209%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/12/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/121221321749/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1aed432e/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/121221321749/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1aed432e/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=XR2WNtr-w7M:HBLeDBLTF-4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=XR2WNtr-w7M:HBLeDBLTF-4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feed